modmod <- brm(whole ~ site,
                  family=Gamma(link="log"),
                  data=newest %>% filter(whole>0),
                  prior=c(prior(normal(-1,0.001), class="b"),
                          prior(normal(0.1, 0.05), class="Intercept")),
                  #sample_prior="only",
                  iter=1000, chains=1,
                  file="modmod.rds",
                  file_refit="on_change")
